NG0409:425: 'on kyang gdul bya'i dbang gis so sor snang *//
NG0409:426: de nyid dam pa'i don la mthong ba med //

NG0409:428: de bzhin nyid du sbyar bas don dang 'gal //

NG0409:447: rgyu 'bras rigs 'byed gzung 'dzin mtshan ma can //

NG0409:675: dus dang gnas dang mdzad pa dang *//

NG0409:694: nyams dang rtag tu ci la @#//

NG0409:725: e ma ye shes gnyis med byang chub sems //

NG0409:744: mi 'gyur nam mkha'i rang bzhin las //

NG0409:746: mkha' dang sprin ltar ye gnas pas //

NG0409:750: mi sbro mi 'dug gzhan ma yin //
NG0409:751: thig le ye nas rdo rje dbyings //

NG0409:754: stong dri brdal chen zhing gnas pa //

NG0409:756: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od brdal yang *//
NG0409:757: byang chub sems las gzhan pa med //
NG0409:758: gang ga'i rgyal rigs 'dzin pa yang *//
NG0409:759: dbyings su gcig pas 'du ba med //
NG0409:760: ji snyed theg pa mtha' yas kyang *//
NG0409:763: snying po snying po bcud kyi mchog / theg pa'i theg pa yang dag don //
NG0409:764: ma bcos ma bslad chos kyi dbyings //

NG0409:770: ched byas med pas rang bzhin ngang *//
NG0409:771: ma chags thabs kyis spyod pas na //

NG0409:773: kha dog dbyibs grangs la sogs pa //
NG0409:774: rtsi las 'das phyir dmigs dang bral //
NG0409:775: dmigs bral snying po'i don 'don pas //

NG0409:777: brjod pa med pa'i gsung nyid do //
NG0409:778: rtog bral snying po don la brtag / e ma ngo mtshar rmad du byung *//
NG0409:779: mi dmigs pa las dmigs pa bral //

NG0409:782: de bzhin nyid du dmigs pa med //
NG0409:784: chos kyi rtsa ba nyid yin te //
NG0409:785: rtsa ba'i rtsa ba rgyu yi rgyu //
NG0409:786: kun gyi dgongs pa ngo mtshar che //
NG0409:787: mkha' ldan yang dog gnyis med ldan //
NG0409:788: rgyal ba'i dgogs pa spros pa med //
NG0409:789: ma byas gzugs brnyan kun 'byung ba //
NG0409:790: 'gag med ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NG0409:791: rdo rje rin chen kun 'dus legs //
NG0409:792: dpag med thig le rgyas pa legs //
NG0409:793: chags med mkha' 'dra dag pa legs //
NG0409:794: don grub rdo rje gsang ba legs //
NG0409:796: byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' rgya mtsho chen po'i rgyud las /

NG0409:798: thig ler kun 'dus thig le lung *//
NG0409:799: rtse gcig bsdus pa'i bla na med //
NG0409:800: chos kyi snying po kun gyi don //

NG0409:802: bya bral bde klong ji bzhin mchog / snying rje nam mkha'i yul las 'das //

NG0409:804: thig le mi 'gyur bde chen klong *//
NG0409:805: bstod cing bsngags pa kun las 'das //

NG0409:808: bya bral bde chen nam mkha'i klong *//

NG0409:811: spros med bsam pa'i yul las 'das //
NG0409:812: dbang po'i spyod yul ma yin zhing *//
NG0409:813: tshig dang yi ge de bzhin min //
NG0409:814: brtag dka' brjod du rdul tsam med //
NG0409:815: bsam med bsam pa'i ngang 'jog pa //
NG0409:816: bde chen rlung nas gol bar 'gyur //
NG0409:817: ming tshig sgra yi rjes 'brang bas //
NG0409:818: mi mthong smig sgyu snyeg pa 'dra //
NG0409:820: ci phyir ye nas mtshon du med //
NG0409:821: bde sdug mnyam 'dres dag pa'i tshul //
NG0409:822: rnam pa mi mjed thabs kyis rol //
NG0409:823: gsal la ma 'dres bsam kun bral //
NG0409:827: mthong ba mig med mngon sum yin //
NG0409:828: mtha' dbus bral ba yangs pa'i spyan //
NG0409:829: snang brtags rang snang chos kun ni //
NG0409:830: mi g.yo mi 'dor mnyam par gnas //
NG0409:831: mi dgongs rol pa thabs kyi sku //
NG0409:832: thun mong ma yin thabs che yang *//
NG0409:833: kun gyis yangs pa'i nyon mongs rnams //
NG0409:834: mtshams med la sogs spyod pas kyang *//
NG0409:835: don dam gnyis med bde ba grub //
NG0409:836: 'dod chags la sogs de bzhin no //
NG0409:837: lung rigs thun mong don mtshon nas //
NG0409:838: rnam tri ting 'dzin rim bsgoms pas //
NG0409:839: rtsol bral mnyam pa'i don las gol //
NG0409:840: bya bral nam mkha'i mtha' la gnas //
NG0409:841: rang byung ye shes snyad dang bral //
NG0409:842: zin pa'i bdud rtsis rtsol ba 'joms //
NG0409:843: bya bral yul la ye nas gnas //
NG0409:844: thams cad thig le skye med pas //
NG0409:846: dngos med skye 'gag bral ba'ang med //
NG0409:847: mtshan ma med pas cir mi gnas //
NG0409:848: bya bral bde ba'i snying po 'di //
NG0409:849: nam mkha'i mtha' bzhin ye gnas pas //

NG0409:865: ma brtags ma bsams mnyam pa nyid //
NG0409:866: dag pa'i don la der gnas pa //
NG0409:867: ma bcos rnam dag rgya mtsho'i gling *//
NG0409:868: yon tan dpag med dbyer med klong *//
NG0409:869: ji bzhin don chen mnyam pa la //
NG0409:870: gang yang med de sna tshogs 'byung *//

NG0409:894: gang yang dang blang dor ba med //
NG0409:896: dam pa'i don chen nam mkha' 'dra //
NG0409:897: don la de ltar gnas pa gces //
NG0409:899: byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' rgya mtsho chen po'i rgyud las /

NG0409:904: rnam dag bde chen ngang la gnas //
NG0409:905: mnyam nyid kun bzang nyid kyi dbyings //
NG0409:906: bde gshegs gsung sgra kun la sogs //
NG0409:907: mkha' ltar gnas pas a rab bde //
NG0409:908: rdzogs chen ma bgrod phyin pa'i lam //
NG0409:909: byar med bde chen lhun rdzogs dbyings //
NG0409:910: theg pa tha dad rim snang ba //

NG0409:912: rgyal thabs spyi blugs kun gyi rtog / shes bya'i shes bya kun gyi gzhi //

NG0409:915: bde chen rnam dag byang chub dbyings //

NG0409:917: kun bzang rang byung bcom ldan 'das //
NG0409:918: gcig bu rgyal pa'i rje btsun mchog / sku gsung
NG0409:919: thugs kyi phyag rgya'i mchog / bla na med pa'i
NG0409:920: mchog la gnas // chos dbyings ma skyes kun 'byung bas //
NG0409:921: rig pa rgya mtsho lhun gyis grub //
NG0409:922: lhun rdzogs byang chub sems kyi dbyings //
NG0409:923: mi gnas 'bras bu'i ngo bor gnas //
NG0409:925: ye nas rgya mtsho dbyings dang mtshungs //
NG0409:926: spro bsdu ye nas ji bzhin ngang *//
NG0409:927: bsod nams ye shes dus gcig rdzogs //
NG0409:928: lta ba nam mkha' lta bur brtag / btang snyoms lhun rdzogs chos kyi dbyings //
NG0409:929: mi gnas nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NG0409:930: thugs rje'i cho 'phrul ya mtshan che /
NG0409:931: khyung chen mkha' la 'phyo ba bzhin //
NG0409:932: chu klung ngam 'grogs nyam mi nga *//
NG0409:933: bar snang stong pa lam du bde //
NG0409:934: gang du dmigs pa dus gcig gcog / de nyid ye sbyang rnal 'byor thugs //
NG0409:935: byang chub snying po nyid rtogs pa //
NG0409:936: sangs rgyas ye nas grub pa'i ngang *//
NG0409:937: da gdod btsal du ga la yod //
NG0409:938: re dogs mtha' las rnam par 'das //
NG0409:939: de rtogs yon tan bsam las 'das //
NG0409:940: bdag gzhan don kun lhun rdzogs pa //
NG0409:941: spyod pa rgya mtsho bder spyad kyang *//
NG0409:942: mi gos dogs med pad+ma bzhin //
NG0409:943: chos nyid chags med rtog gyur na //
NG0409:944: spyad pas gang spyad nyams pa med //
NG0409:945: thugs rjes spyod pa mtha' yangs pa //
NG0409:946: thabs kyi spyod pa de bzhin spyod //
NG0409:947: rnam rtog sbros bral 'dzin mi mnga' //
NG0409:948: mkha' mnyam rgyal po re ba bskang *//
NG0409:949: ci spyad ci smra gang 'byung ba //
NG0409:950: skye med dbyings kyi cho 'phrul rnams //
NG0409:953: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yangs pa na //
NG0409:954: lhun grub rin chen gzhal yas khang *//
NG0409:955: de las rgya mtsho bsam las 'das //
NG0409:956: rang la rang nyid skur ston pa //
NG0409:957: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor rnams //
NG0409:959: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs su 'phro //
NG0409:960: sprin med mkha' la gza' skar ltar //
NG0409:961: rgyal tshogs bsam 'das cir yang snang *//
NG0409:962: ma spangs rol mdzad longs spyod ldan //
NG0409:963: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal sbyor ba //
NG0409:964: shes rab dbyings las phyag rgyar gsal //
NG0409:965: sa le mnyam la ma 'dres pa /
NG0409:966: khyad par ye shes sgyu ma'i tshogs //
NG0409:967: kun tu bzang po rang byung ba //
NG0409:968: gcig pu mnyam nyid chos kyi sku //
NG0409:969: sku gsung lhun rdzogs phyag rgya che //
NG0409:970: ye nas lhun grub byang chub mchog / bla med mchog la zhugs pa yin //
NG0409:971: bdag gzhan mi rtog ma 'dres gsal //
NG0409:972: rdo rje nyi ma shar ba bzhin //
NG0409:973: lhan ne gsal ba'i 'od dang ldan //
NG0409:974: rnam thar dbu tri phyag shong ste //
NG0409:975: ye shes drug ldan chos kyi dbyings //
NG0409:976: skar tshogs bsam yas mkhar 'dus ltar //
NG0409:977: bsam yas dkyil 'khor chos kyi dbyings //
NG0409:978: nyi ma gza' skar zil gnon ltar //
NG0409:979: theg dman zil gnon ye sangs rgyas //

NG0409:982: dkyil 'khor 'od lnga kun gyi bdag / kun gzhi rnam dag ye shes klong *//
NG0409:983: rang byung ye shes btsal med ngang *//
NG0409:984: stong khams kun snyoms thugs rje mchog / 'gro ba'i don mdzad kun tu bzang *//
NG0409:985: dbye gsal blang dor gnyis med don //
NG0409:986: gcig dang du ma rdzun pa'i phyir //
NG0409:987: rnam dag chos dbyings dag pa'i ngang *//
NG0409:989: byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' rgya mtsho chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0409:990: 'byed pa med pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o //    // kye sems dpa' chen po /
NG0409:991: mi gnas mi spyod yongs kyi lam //
NG0409:992: ma rtog rtog par byed pa med //
NG0409:993: thug med dbyings la bri ba med //
NG0409:994: skye med dbyings las skye ba'i mchog / gang yang ma yin chos kyi dbyings /
NG0409:995: khams gsum rnam dag skye med dbyings //
NG0409:996: dbus mtha' mi dmigs rtogs las 'das //
NG0409:997: rtog pa'i gnyan por mi rtog sgom //
NG0409:998: mi rtog sgom pa rtog pa'i nad //
NG0409:999: chos dbyings rtog pa las 'das pa //
NG0409:1000: rtog dang mi rtog gnyis ka mtha' //
NG0409:1001: spros med byang chub snying po ni //
NG0409:1002: kun gzhi rnam dag ye shes zhing *//
NG0409:1003: chos dbyings dam tshig lha dang bdag / lta spyod la sogs tha snyad rnams //
NG0409:1004: 'du na ye shes bde ba'i zhing *//
NG0409:1005: bud+d+ha sems can ye gcig pa //
NG0409:1006: dbyings dang ye shes tha snyad tsam //
NG0409:1007: ngo bo chos sku snying po'i tshul //
NG0409:1008: sa la bgrod rtsol lam dang bral //
NG0409:1009: ting 'dzin bskyed cing dmigs pa med //
NG0409:1010: dam tshig bsrung ba'i tshul du med //
NG0409:1014: dkyil 'khor byang chub sems las byung *//
NG0409:1015: skye 'gag med pa'i ngo bo la //
NG0409:1017: mthun 'jug spyod pa kun mdzad kyang *//
NG0409:1018: snying po don la g.yo ba med //
NG0409:1020: thugs rje 'gro don kun la bdal //
NG0409:1021: mig tshig sgrol mas don mtshon pa //
NG0409:1022: rnam grangs bsam yas blo la gnas //
NG0409:1023: de bzhin mnyam nyid nges pa'i don //
NG0409:1024: mi tshogs bsam yas gcig tu 'dus //
NG0409:1025: yod med rtag chad ma yin la //
NG0409:1026: bdag dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa med //
NG0409:1027: phyi nang gzung 'dzin mtha' dang bral //
NG0409:1028: gang zhig de ltar rtog byed pa //
NG0409:1029: mi mkhas blun po phyi rol pa //
NG0409:1030: snang yang med par gang smra ba //
NG0409:1031: mu stegs chad pa'i lam yin no //
NG0409:1032: de nyid don la blo zhan pa //
NG0409:1034: gang yang ma yin sna tshogs pa //
NG0409:1035: 'byung phyir ye shes chos dbyings mchog / snying po byang chub bcom med lam //
NG0409:1036: 'du na don rtogs rdzogs chen pa //
NG0409:1037: rnam dag grub pa rtog med mkha' //
NG0409:1038: re dogs med pas dbyings nyid gsal //
NG0409:1039: 'bras bu btsal bas grub mtha' med //
NG0409:1040: kun gzhi ye shes chos kyi dbyings //
NG0409:1042: gang nas su la gsol ba 'debs //
NG0409:1043: nyam thag btsal bas grub pa med //
NG0409:1044: chos nyid chos 'tshol ga la rnyed //
NG0409:1046: rgya mtsho dbyings nas smig sgyu rnyed //
NG0409:1047: btsal bas mi rnyed ngal don chung *//
NG0409:1048: ye nas byang chub snying po las //
NG0409:1049: btsal zhing don mtha' sems la thug / ting 'dzin byang chub sems la gsal //
NG0409:1050: brtags na bdag nyid bud+ha dbyings //
NG0409:1051: mnyam nyid chos sku mchog nyid gter //
NG0409:1052: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor rmad byung ba //
NG0409:1053: snying po don mchog dbyings la 'dus //
NG0409:1054: bsod nams ye shes lhun rdzogs pa //
NG0409:1055: mtshan dang dpe byad ye shes 'das //
NG0409:1056: chos nyid khyab bdal snyoms pa'i mgon //
NG0409:1057: ye nas byang chub snying po'i don //
NG0409:1058: rgyal ba nyid dang dgongs ba gcig / mnyes ldan dngos grub brjod mi lang *//
NG0409:1059: 'jig rten nyi mas gsal byed ltar //
NG0409:1060: ma lus snang byed theg pa'i mchog / rgya mtsho u dum wa ra bzhin //
NG0409:1061: byang chub sems ldan don rtogs na //
NG0409:1063: chags sdang blang dor blo skyes te //
NG0409:1065: byang chub don las 'gal ba'i phyir //
NG0409:1066: skad cig grub pa'i rgyu nyid la //
NG0409:1067: log rtog gso zhug 'khros pas brlag / 'bad thag chad 'gyur 'grub mi 'gyur //
NG0409:1068: blo ldan 'gyod pa skyes gyur na //
NG0409:1069: rang sems dpang btsugs ma gtong bas //
NG0409:1070: byang chub sems mchog blo la shar //
NG0409:1071: bskal par bsags pa'i mun nag nyid //
NG0409:1072: rig pa'i rgyal po nyi zer gyis //
NG0409:1073: skad cig nyid kyis sel bar 'gyur //
NG0409:1074: blun rmongs sems rgyud tha dad pa //
NG0409:1077: rgyal ba'i sku ru gcig pa la //
NG0409:1078: 'khrul pas so sor brtags mthong nor //
NG0409:1079: ye shes sgyu ma rgyal ba dang *//
NG0409:1081: brtags pas tha dad snang ba yang *//
NG0409:1082: don dam dbyings su yongs kyis mnyam //
NG0409:1084: byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' rgya mtsho chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0409:1085: sgom zhing bsam du med pa'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o //    // kye sems dpa' chen po /
NG0409:1086: gang la mi gnas mya ngan 'das //
NG0409:1087: ye nas byang chub snying po la //
NG0409:1088: rang sems bud+ha mngon sum pa //
NG0409:1089: gzhan du btsal ba rdul yang med //
NG0409:1090: 'gro ba skal ldan rnams don du //
NG0409:1091: mi sgrub gzhag pa nyid du'ang med //
NG0409:1092: chos dbyings dam pa'i don rig na //
NG0409:1093: kun la khyab pa'i thugs rje 'byung *//
NG0409:1094: sgyu ma thabs mkhas ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0409:1095: 'gro don spyod pa sna tshogs ston //
NG0409:1096: bdag gzhan spyod pa mi 'byed phyir //
NG0409:1098: d+harma ka ya skye na rtog pa yis //
NG0409:1099: skye ba'i cho 'phrul cir yang bstan //
NG0409:1100: mdzad pa bcu gnyis don ston pa //
NG0409:1101: cir yang 'gyur ba med pa sprul pa'i sku //
NG0409:1102: thugs rje cho 'phrul cir yang gsal //
NG0409:1103: thugs rjes gdul bya kun 'dul ba //
NG0409:1104: sgyu ma'i rlom sems kun dang bral //
NG0409:1105: rgya ba'i dgongs pa ji snyed pa //
NG0409:1106: rang bzhin ma bcos de bzhin nyid //
NG0409:1107: d+harma sarba sgyu ma lta bu'i phyir //
NG0409:1108: ting 'dzin sgyu ma sna tshogs rnams //
NG0409:1109: gang du'ang mi dmigs nyes pa med //
NG0409:1110: rang byung rmad grags snying po ni //
NG0409:1111: gang ltar bstan kyang 'gyur med ngang *//
NG0409:1112: phyi nang ma lus gzugs rnams ni //
NG0409:1113: sku mchog brgyan gyi 'khor lor rdzogs //
NG0409:1114: sgra skad bsam yas ma lus pa //
NG0409:1115: ye nas spros med gsung gi mchog / thams cad dbyings su ro gcig pa //
NG0409:1116: thugs mchog mi zad rgyan gyi mchog / srid dri mnyam sbyor mi g.yo ba //
NG0409:1117: chos sku snying po byang chub mchog / gsang sngags dbang phyug go 'phang ldan //
NG0409:1118: man ngag gsang ba'i don med par //
NG0409:1119: dregs ldan nga rgyal che ba'i sa //
NG0409:1120: rang gi lta ba mthong 'dod pas //
NG0409:1121: gti mug 'thibs pa zon med pas //
NG0409:1122: yas bzhag btsan thabs drigs pa yis //
NG0409:1124: brnyas sems mnyam las 'gal ba'i phyir //
NG0409:1125: lta spyod bdud kyi las su 'gyur //
NG0409:1126: mtho dman rlom sems mnyam pa'i bcugs //
NG0409:1127: mkhas pa don gyi lung bzhin du //
NG0409:1128: skyon ldan dge rtsa khyad par 'phags //
NG0409:1129: tshig la mkhas pa nyid yin kyang *//
NG0409:1130: phyal 'gyur byang chub sems spang na //
NG0409:1131: rdo rje lta bur grub 'dod pa //
NG0409:1132: log 'dren gsog can bden smras kyang *//
NG0409:1134: gsang sngags rgya mtsho sgo yangs zhes //
NG0409:1135: rgyal ba'i sku bslus slar log pa //
NG0409:1136: bdud rtsi dug tu 'gyur ba de //
NG0409:1137: lus sems rdul du gyur pa yis //
NG0409:1138: dmyal bar nges 'gro snying re rje //
NG0409:1141: nges pa'i don la rtse gcig pas //
NG0409:1142: mnyam pa'i gdang las ma g.yos pa //
NG0409:1143: byang chub chen po'i rlung la gnas //
NG0409:1144: bde btsal med pa'i don gsal zhing *//
NG0409:1145: tshad med don ldan rnal 'byor pas //
NG0409:1146: don gzhi ma btsal grub 'dod pa //
NG0409:1147: bya bral lhun grub ngang la gnas //
NG0409:1148: gang la mi chags mi snang zhing *//
NG0409:1149: mnyam pa nyid las mi 'da' ba //
NG0409:1150: rgyal ba'i sras po ngo mtshar che //
NG0409:1151: rig pa 'dzin pa'i don la gnas //
NG0409:1152: de yis sems kyi don bltas pas //
NG0409:1153: mthong ba med pa'i don la gnas //
NG0409:1154: gang zhig dad ldan stong pa de //
NG0409:1155: theg mchog rigs su nges pa dang *//
NG0409:1156: ma rmongs lhag pa'i don shes las //
NG0409:1157: gzhan du brjod na tshig par 'gyur //
NG0409:1159: byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' rgya mtsho chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0409:1160: don dang mtshan ma bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o //    // kye sems dpa' chen po /
NG0409:1161: ma bcos ma byas dag pa la //
NG0409:1162: gdod med rtsol ba ye nas med //
NG0409:1163: med pa'i rgyud las yod gsal ba //
NG0409:1164: ma mthong 'dres pa'i dkyil 'khor mchog / dang po med pa'i rgyu yin na //
NG0409:1165: de la rtog pa'i rdzas ci yod //
NG0409:1166: de bas dam pa'i lung nyid la //
NG0409:1167: rtog ges spyad par mi 'grub ste //
NG0409:1168: rang gi don yang nyams gyur phyir //
NG0409:1169: brtag cing spyad par mi bya'o //
NG0409:1170: yod med dag la rab brtags pas //
NG0409:1171: stong pas don la mjal 'dod pa //
NG0409:1173: 'grub par mi 'gyur rang rgyud rlag / ji ltar nyi ma'i 'od zer la //
NG0409:1174: mig gis brtag par mi nus kyis //
NG0409:1175: de nyid mun pa snang ba ltar //
NG0409:1176: e ma rab tu gsang ba yis //
NG0409:1178: ma yin de nyid bdag gi bu //
NG0409:1179: rigs 'di ma bcos de lta bu //
NG0409:1180: gsang sngags rgya mtsho chen po 'di //
NG0409:1181: lung dang rig pa rtog pa dang *//
NG0409:1182: dpe dang tshad ma gtan tshigs dang *//
NG0409:1183: rjes su dpags pa'i shes rab kyis //
NG0409:1184: rtog par nus pa ma yin te //
NG0409:1185: dngos grub rlabs chen 'khrigs pa can //
NG0409:1186: bsam yas gting ni dpag dka' ba //
NG0409:1187: lung dang man ngag theb pas grub //
NG0409:1189: don med mtshan ma g.yeng ba'i rgyu //
NG0409:1190: rtog med blo ngan phung bar 'gyur //
NG0409:1191: de phyir kun gyi spyod yul min //
NG0409:1192: rdo rje rigs pa 'dzin pa'i sras //
NG0409:1193: lhun gyis grub pa'i spyod yul te //
NG0409:1194: ji ltar nor bu rin chen dang *//
NG0409:1196: e ma rab tu gsang ba yi //
NG0409:1197: dam pa'i spyod yul zab cing phra //
NG0409:1198: gzung du med la brjod dang bral //
NG0409:1199: 'di zhes bstan du ga la yod //
NG0409:1200: e ma bya btsal med pa la //
NG0409:1201: btsal bas chu bos 'bogs byed pa //
NG0409:1202: rab tu bcings pas dam bcings pa //
NG0409:1203: rtsol ba don med ngal ba'i rgyu //
NG0409:1204: e ma ho lhun grub snying po la /
NG0409:1205: khrus dang gtsang spra bya mi dgos //
NG0409:1206: dka' thub spyad pa'ang mi dgos te //
NG0409:1207: don dam bde chen lhun grub ngang *//
NG0409:1210: ye nas mun pa ma grub phyir //
NG0409:1211: btsal med bde chen snying po la //
NG0409:1212: mtha' yi mun pa ye nas med //
NG0409:1213: e ma ho don gyis don btsal bas //
NG0409:1214: don la brtag med de bzhin nyid //
NG0409:1215: de phyir rnyed pa'i gnas med de //
NG0409:1216: mkha' la 'dud ltar gting dpag dka' //
NG0409:1217: e ma'o bde chen snying po la //
NG0409:1218: sgro skur ched byas don gyis tshol //
NG0409:1219: btsal bas ma rnyed rang la thug / rang yang de bzhin nyid kyis zhi //
NG0409:1220: e maho rgyal ba'i spyod yul 'di //
NG0409:1221: sus kyang ma sbas rang bzhin gsang *//
NG0409:1222: nam mkha'i mtha' ltar dbyer med par //
NG0409:1223: nyi ma sgrib med ji bzhin no //
NG0409:1224: e maho ngo mtshar rmad kyis chos *//
NG0409:1225: kun la gnas la rang bzhin gsang *//
NG0409:1226: mnyam nyid rig pa'i spyod yul te //
NG0409:1227: skyes bu blo btsal rab kyis rtogs //
NG0409:1228: e maho nam mkha' dag pa'i mtha' //
NG0409:1229: mkha' ltar nyi snang kun la khyab //
NG0409:1230: spros med nyi ma'i snying po la //
NG0409:1231: rnam rtog mun pas ga la 'grib //
NG0409:1232: e maho stong nyid byang chub sems //
NG0409:1233: ma bcos kun gzhi gzhal yas su //
NG0409:1234: nyi ma stong gi dkyil 'khor shar //
NG0409:1235: kun la khyab cing yongs su snubs //
NG0409:1236: ma bcos spros med thig le las //
NG0409:1238: cir yang snang la gang du'ang med //
NG0409:1239: byang chub g.yung drung 'gyur ba med //
NG0409:1240: snying po'i snying po theg pa'i rtse //
NG0409:1241: mi 'gyur mi shigs rdo rje'i don //
NG0409:1242: dpa' bo g.yul las bzlog pa'i mchog / mi rnams nam mkha'i mtha' dang bral //
NG0409:1243: yangs shing che ba'i chos chen po //
NG0409:1244: chung ngu rnams kyi gnyen po mchog / ji ltar gcan gzan rgyal po lta //
NG0409:1245: chung ngu zil gnon stobs po che //
NG0409:1246: 'khrul pas sna tshogs brtag pa yang *//
NG0409:1247: drang ba'i don las ma rtogs pa //
NG0409:1248: nges pa'i don du gcig las med //
NG0409:1249: gcig po mtha' bral nam mkha'i ngang *//
NG0409:1251: snying po de la 'da' ba med //
NG0409:1253: byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' rgya mtsho chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0409:1254: khyad par chen po'i le'u ste bco lnga pa'o //      // kye sems dpa' chen po /
NG0409:1255: chos sku skye med mya ngan 'das //
NG0409:1257: nga med bdag bral mnyam pa'i thugs //
NG0409:1258: rin chen gter 'dus rgyal ba'i sku //
NG0409:1259: ma spangs ma bsgrubs mkha' ltar gnas /
NG0409:1260: khams tri brtags pas sems kyi dbyings //
NG0409:1261: sna tshogs rang bzhin dbye ba med //
NG0409:1262: rgya mtsho'i rlabs ltar g.yo ba 'byung *//
NG0409:1263: chos dbyings skye med yul gyi ngang *//
NG0409:1264: phyag rgya skye ba'i cho 'phrul can //
NG0409:1265: 'khor ba bcos med dgongs pa'i phyir //
NG0409:1266: rang byung dbyings las ma g.yos kyang *//
NG0409:1269: don dam dbyings nyid rdzogs pa che //
NG0409:1270: snying po nyi ma 'od kyi mchog / sku gsung thugs kyi 'khor lo can //
NG0409:1271: thams cad dbyer med rgya mtsho 'dra //
NG0409:1275: brtags pas bdag nyid rol pa'i ngang *//
NG0409:1276: 'chi med bdud rtsi sman gyi mchog / rang la rdzogs pas btsal mi dgos //
NG0409:1277: rgyu gcig chos dbyings mnyam pa'i ngang *//
NG0409:1278: rang bzhin sems nyid gsal ba'i dbyings //
NG0409:1280: zhen med sems nyid yum gyi mchog / 'du na nga la mi gnas pas //
NG0409:1281: thabs dang shes rab 'brel bar gnas //
NG0409:1282: phyag rgya'i rol pa bsam mi khyab //
NG0409:1283: rang bzhin med las cir yang snang *//
NG0409:1284: byang chub ngang du kun 'dus pa //
NG0409:1285: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya mtsho 'dra //
NG0409:1286: 'byung ba'i skar tshogs bsam mi khyab //
NG0409:1287: mkha' mnyam dbang phyug rgyal po'i thugs //
NG0409:1288: yon tan rgyal chog kun gyi ngang *//
NG0409:1289: bdag med phyogs bral chos dbyings mkha' //
NG0409:1290: sems can rnams la mi gnyis kyang *//
NG0409:1291: thugs rjes 'gro drug gnas nas sgrol //
NG0409:1292: mtho dman med par yongs la bdal //
NG0409:1293: chos nyid nam mkha' dri med klong *//
NG0409:1294: srid gsum 'gran zla med pa'i mchog / gang la'ang mi g.yo 'gyur ba med //
NG0409:1295: gang la'ang bsam pa kun dang bral //
NG0409:1296: 'di zhes bsam pa'i rigs dang bral //
NG0409:1297: gcig la gcig pa'i mtha' dang bral //
NG0409:1298: rigs dang phyogs su gzung du med //
NG0409:1299: mnyam rdzogs lhun gyi sku mnga' zhing *//
NG0409:1300: rigs med bdag nyid chen po mchog / mnyam nyid mkha' la rol ba'i sku //
NG0409:1301: mi gnas bde chen mnyam nyid rlung *//
NG0409:1302: 'di la rtag dang chad pa med //
NG0409:1303: yod med phyogs ris gzung med cing *//
NG0409:1304: 'dzin pa med de de bzhin nyid //
NG0409:1305: chos brgyad snyoms par don gsal ba //
NG0409:1306: ye nas mnyam pa'i don rig pa'o //
NG0409:1307: gsang sngags rdo rje nam mkha' che //
NG0409:1308: kun gyi spyod yul ma yin te //
NG0409:1309: gsang chen brtag dka' thun mong min //
NG0409:1310: rdo rje sems dpa'i spyod yul te //
NG0409:1311: gnas ni nam mkha'i dbyings la gnas /
NG0409:1312: khyab ni snang srid kun la khyab //
NG0409:1313: yod ni rdul yang med pa ste //
NG0409:1314: bstan ni kun la mthun par bstan //
NG0409:1315: 'bras bu btsal ba med par thug / sku ni snying po byang chub ste //
NG0409:1316: gsung ni ngo bo nam mkha'i gsung *//
NG0409:1317: thugs ni stong chen mkha' ltar bdal //
NG0409:1318: yon tan nam mkha'i gter ltar che //
NG0409:1320: thugs rje 'khor ba khyab par gzigs //
NG0409:1321: skyon bral nyag gcig dbyings kyi gter //
NG0409:1322: dbyings dang ye shes tha snyad pas //
NG0409:1323: mi gnas gnas la gnas pa med //
NG0409:1324: thugs mtha' med pa'i klong chen mtsho //
NG0409:1325: spros bral mnyam nyid ji bzhin gter //
NG0409:1326: mkha' ltar gnas so khyab pa'i sku //
NG0409:1328: thams cad snying po byang chub sku //
NG0409:1330: rang the ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin //
NG0409:1331: snang bas ngo mtshar rmad du byung *//
NG0409:1332: zab mo bya bral rdzogs pa'i lung *//
NG0409:1335: spros med lung dang kun 'dus lung *//
NG0409:1336: sbyor sgrol mnyam rtog ma bcings lung *//
NG0409:1337: mnyam nyid rig pa gter gyi lung *//
NG0409:1338: sku gsung thugs sogs chos kun gyi //
NG0409:1339: thob zin mthong zin sbyangs pa zin //
NG0409:1340: mchod dang zhugs dang dbang thob pas //
NG0409:1341: btsal med ye nas byas pa'i lung *//
NG0409:1342: mi bya med de kun bkag cing *//
NG0409:1343: spyod pas lhun grub mnyam nyid gter //
NG0409:1344: ye shes zang ma'i bdag nyid de //
NG0409:1346: lhun grub bya bral rdzogs pa'i lung *//
NG0409:1348: byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' rgya mtsho chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0409:1349: tshe 'phrul btsal med bya bral lung gi le'u ste
NG0409:1350: bcu drug pa'o // // de nas rab tu bshad
NG0409:1351: bya ba // sems dpa' chen po mkha' mnyam sku //
NG0409:1352: mtha' dbus don bral snying po don //
NG0409:1353: nges don nges pa bshad bya'i phyir //
NG0409:1354: nges pa rtag dang mi rtag pa //
NG0409:1355: brtag dka' nyi zer lta bu'i don //
NG0409:1356: gang zhig nges par 'grub pa na //
NG0409:1357: de la brtag bya ma grub pa //
NG0409:1358: yod dang med ces ci byar yod //
NG0409:1359: snying po'i snying po kun 'dus pa //
NG0409:1360: de la mtha' dbus bdag gzhan med //
NG0409:1361: gang zhig gang gis mthong mi rung *//
NG0409:1362: rtag pa dag dang mi rtag pa //
NG0409:1363: de yang mtshan ma'i tha snyad tsam //
NG0409:1364: nor bu rin chen 'dod dgu'i mdzod //
NG0409:1365: cir yang med la cir yang snang *//
NG0409:1366: snying po'i don las gang 'da' ba //
NG0409:1367: rgyal ba'ang than pas brlag 'gyur na //
NG0409:1368: sa sbyong sems dpa' smos ci dgos //
NG0409:1370: gcig dang tha dad gang brtags pa //
NG0409:1372: grol dang bcings min bden min dang *//
NG0409:1373: grub min ngo bo gcig pa la //
NG0409:1374: ltos pa'i rtog pas rab tu phye //
NG0409:1375: gcig dang tha dad las grol te //
NG0409:1376: 'du ru snang yang mtha' dang bral //
NG0409:1377: zhen pa med na bde ba che //
NG0409:1378: bde ba che zhing nor che la //
NG0409:1379: 'jig rten dbang po khams gsum mchog / gsum phyir gsum snang gsum gyi ngang *//
NG0409:1380: dgu ste gcig 'dus thig le'i ngang *//
NG0409:1381: gcig pas spong len bya dang bral //
NG0409:1382: stong pas mnyam brtags las 'das pa //
NG0409:1383: dmigs las 'das pas brtag tu med //
NG0409:1384: tshig las 'das pas brjod dang bral //
NG0409:1385: gad+ga klung gi rgyal ba yang *//
NG0409:1386: stong nyid mnyam pa rol mdzad cing *//
NG0409:1387: ji ltar zla brnyan 'char ba ltar //
NG0409:1388: cir yang snang zhing gcig gi ngang *//
NG0409:1389: mtshe dang ldang ldeng lu ma dang *//
NG0409:1390: 'bab chu la sogs mtha' yas pa //
NG0409:1391: rgya mtsho 'du ba ji bzhin du //
NG0409:1392: dus gsum rgyal ba gcig gi ngang *//
NG0409:1393: sprin dang zla ba gza' skar dang *//
NG0409:1394: cho 'phrul nam mkha'i rang bzhin ltar //
NG0409:1395: sems can ngan song mtha' yas kun //
NG0409:1396: snying po byang chub gser dpe bzhin //
NG0409:1397: rtsa dang 'bru dang lo tog dang *//
NG0409:1398: sman dang dug tu snang ba yang *//
NG0409:1399: nus mthu kha dog dbyibs mtha' yas //
NG0409:1400: sa gzhi la ni tha dad med //
NG0409:1403: kun byed dbyings nyid byang chub sems //
NG0409:1404: ngam 'grogs chu dang g.yang sa dang *//
NG0409:1405: med dang sprul dang gcan gzan dug / mi dang srin po shan pa yang *//
NG0409:1406: bya la ya nga g.yang sa med //
NG0409:1407: de bzhin bde sdug rtsol mi rtsol //
NG0409:1408: lam drug thabs dgu 'bras bu dgu //
NG0409:1409: bde sdug btang snyoms la sogs pa //
NG0409:1410: snang yang rdzogs chen yang nga bral //
NG0409:1411: ji ltar kha zas tha dad pa /
NG0409:1412: kha dog dbyibs ldan mdzes gyur pa //
NG0409:1413: ro med tshim pa ma yin ltar //
NG0409:1414: rdzogs mchog med pa'i sman pa rnams //
NG0409:1415: btsal yang long bas long ba khrid //
NG0409:1416: ro med kha zas de bzhin no //
NG0409:1417: de phyir mnyam nyid snying po la //
NG0409:1418: btud de don la bltas gsal ba //
NG0409:1419: gang la'ang ma yin de bzhin no //
NG0409:1420: bstan pas rdo rje ri zom bzhin //

NG0409:1424: mnyam pas rig pa'i skyes bu bzhin //

NG0409:1426: re skong yid bzhin nor bu sbyin //
NG0409:1427: mi 'gyur brtan pas gser bzhin te //

NG0409:1429: bud+d+ha kun dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NG0409:1431: 'das pas rgyal ba nyid kyang brlag / gang la 'di las mi 'da' zhing *//

NG0409:1519: skyes bu mchog gi spyod yul bas //
